text: The Harmanec Tunnel () is a railway tunnel on the Banská Bystrica - Dolná Štubňa track. It is long and it is the longest railway tunnel in Slovakia. It was built from 1936 to 1940. ==See also== *Bujanov Tunnel ==Sources== *On the ridge of the Greater Fatra Category:Railway tunnels in Slovakia Category:Tunnels completed in 1940
title: Harmanec Tunnel
